"""Migrate Claude agent definitions to Codex-compatible markdown or TOML.

Transforms .claude/agents/*.md (YAML frontmatter + body) into
.codex/agents/*.toml (native Codex custom agent config) or
.codex/agents/*.md (backward-compatible pure markdown).

Reuses MCP namespace normalization and primitive mapping from the shared
migration support package.

Usage:
  python3 .codex/skills/migrate-agents-to-codex/scripts/migrate_claude_agents_to_codex.py --agent example-agent-a
  python3 .codex/skills/migrate-agents-to-codex/scripts/migrate_claude_agents_to_codex.py --all --format toml
  python3 .codex/skills/migrate-agents-to-codex/scripts/migrate_claude_agents_to_codex.py --all --dry-run --format toml
"""

